other parts of the United States.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:21.910
This is quite extraordinary and so,
that was the genesis for this book,

00:06:21.910 --> 00:06:25.770
to try and understand
why so many people think

00:06:25.770 --> 00:06:29.090
that they have Cherokee ancestry
in their family and I do apologize

00:06:29.090 --> 00:06:32.120
to Carrie for scooping you
on that <i>Slate </i>article.

00:06:32.120 --> 00:06:37.070
But I do believe there's much more
to be written about this topic.

00:06:37.070 --> 00:06:41.680
I don't believe that anything that
I had written or other scholars

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:45.520
