the Civil War are cast

00:41:11.650 --> 00:41:14.130
out of the Nation during
this period.

00:41:14.130 --> 00:41:20.620
Their evidence, no matter how
clear it is of Cherokee ancestry

00:41:20.620 --> 00:41:27.960
or connection to Cherokee citizens
is deemed never quite good enough

00:41:27.960 --> 00:41:30.770
by most of the commissioners.

00:41:30.770 --> 00:41:37.410
